"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Getting Started\\n\\nDeterministic kernel for multi-agent orchestration via git worktrees.\\n\\n## Install\\n\\n```bash\\nuv pip install -e .\\n```\\n\\nRequires Python 3.12+, git.\\n\\n## Usage\\n\\n```bash\\ndgov init                # Bootstrap .dgov/project.toml\\ndgov run plan.toml       # Execute a plan\\ndgov status              # Show task status\\ndgov watch               # Stream events\\ndgov sentrux check       # Run architectural quality check\\ndgov cleanup             # Annihilate zombie worktrees\\n```\\n\\n## Plan format\\n\\nPlans are TOML files that compile to DAGs:\\n\\n```toml\\n[plan]\\nname = \\\"example\\\"\\n\\n[[unit]]\\nslug = \\\"add-feature\\\"\\nprompt = \\\"Add the feature to src/foo.py\\\"\\nagent = \\\"kimi-k2.5\\\"\\nfiles = [\\\"src/foo.py\\\"]\\n\\n[[unit]]\\nslug = \\\"add-tests\\\"\\nprompt = \\\"Write tests for the feature\\\"\\nagent = \\\"kimi-k2.5\\\"\\nfiles = [\\\"tests/test_foo.py\\\"]\\ndepends_on = [\\\"add-feature\\\"]\\n```\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/getting-started#getting-started\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>Deterministic kernel for multi-agent orchestration via git worktrees.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/getting-started.mdx#getting-started\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nDeterministic kernel for multi-agent orchestration via git worktrees.\\n\",\"title\":\"Getting Started\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/getting-started#install\",\"html\":\"\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">uv</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> pip</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> install</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> -e</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> .</span></span></code></pre>\\n<p>Requires Python 3.12+, git.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/getting-started.mdx#install\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nuv pip install -e .\\nRequires Python 3.12+, git.\\n\",\"title\":\"Install\",\"titles\":[\"Getting Started\"]},{\"href\":\"/getting-started#usage\",\"html\":\"\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">dgov</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> init</span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">                # Bootstrap .dgov/project.toml</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">dgov</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> run</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> plan.toml</span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">       # Execute a plan</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">dgov</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> status</span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">              # Show task status</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">dgov</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> watch</span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">               # Stream events</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">dgov</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> sentrux</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> check</span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">       # Run architectural quality check</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">dgov</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> cleanup</span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">             # Annihilate zombie worktrees</span></span></code></pre>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/getting-started.mdx#usage\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\ndgov init                # Bootstrap .dgov/project.toml\\ndgov run plan.toml       # Execute a plan\\ndgov status              # Show task status\\ndgov watch               # Stream events\\ndgov sentrux check       # Run architectural quality check\\ndgov cleanup             # Annihilate zombie worktrees\\n\",\"title\":\"Usage\",\"titles\":[\"Getting Started\"]},{\"href\":\"/getting-started#plan-format\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Plans are TOML files that compile to DAGs:</p>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">plan</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">name = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;example&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">unit</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">slug = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;add-feature&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">prompt = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;Add the feature to src/foo.py&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">agent = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;kimi-k2.5&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">files = [</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;src/foo.py&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">unit</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">slug = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;add-tests&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">prompt = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;Write tests for the feature&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">agent = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;kimi-k2.5&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">files = [</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;tests/test_foo.py&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">depends_on = [</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;add-feature&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span></code></pre>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/getting-started.mdx#plan-format\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nPlans are TOML files that compile to DAGs:\\n[plan]\\nname = &quot;example&quot;\\n \\n[[unit]]\\nslug = &quot;add-feature&quot;\\nprompt = &quot;Add the feature to src/foo.py&quot;\\nagent = &quot;kimi-k2.5&quot;\\nfiles = [&quot;src/foo.py&quot;]\\n \\n[[unit]]\\nslug = &quot;add-tests&quot;\\nprompt = &quot;Write tests for the feature&quot;\\nagent = &quot;kimi-k2.5&quot;\\nfiles = [&quot;tests/test_foo.py&quot;]\\ndepends_on = [&quot;add-feature&quot;]\",\"title\":\"Plan format\",\"titles\":[\"Getting Started\"]}]}}"
